name: Night of the Living Dead - Feature film

metadata.description: Night of the Living Dead. Full-length Feature Film. Arguably the Worlds 1st Zombie movie! Directed by George A. Romero, this remarkable film features one of the first black leads Duane L. Jones in a mainstream feature film. This Movie still has the power to scare the sh*t out of you. Only 200 available!
